---
const examples = [
  {
    glyph: '{¤}',
    title: 'Friday, 2 AM. Your agent is still reading.',
    body: 'You went to bed. An abject pulled 47 papers from your RSS feeds, ranked them against your open projects, drafted a one-page summary, and pinned it to the canvas. The tokens came from your local Ollama. No surprise bill. No surprise rate limit at hour three. Wake up. Coffee. Read.',
  },
  {
    glyph: '{☾}',
    title: 'Say "show me when the sun sets." A countdown appears.',
    body: 'A small window with an animated sun sliding toward the horizon, counting down the minutes, refreshing itself from live weather data. Nobody wrote an app for this. Nobody ever will. That is the point: it took one sentence, and now it exists, and it is yours.',
  },
  {
    glyph: '{↻}',
    title: 'Your scraper crashed. Twenty seconds later, the work routes around it.',
    body: 'The failed task attaches its error to the goal\'s history. The next planning round reads what just broke, picks a different abject, and stages the retry. No 30-minute chain running off a cliff. The plan rewrites itself round by round.',
  },
  {
    glyph: '{✉}',
    title: 'Your inbox gets sorted before you wake up.',
    body: 'Every morning at eight, an abject reads the night\'s email, separates the clutter from the things that matter, and messages your phone: may I delete these? It waits for your yes. Then, and only then, the junk dies. An assistant with initiative and manners.',
  },
  {
    glyph: '{△}',
    title: 'Click. Your friend\'s cursor is on your canvas.',
    body: 'She\'s in Berlin. You\'re in Brooklyn. Both on Wi-Fi. Pin a note; she draws an arrow to it; you watch her cursor move in real time. End-to-end encrypted WebRTC, ECDH key exchange, AES-256-GCM. The signaling relay never sees a byte.',
  },
  {
    glyph: '{∇}',
    title: 'Twenty words. A new program appears.',
    body: '"Watch ~/Downloads. When a PDF lands, rename it by its title, move it to ~/Papers/{year}." You say it once. The system understands the goal, writes the object, and gives it a face. A new window opens. It is already running.',
  },
];
---

<section id="examples" class="examples-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">What People Build</h2>
    <p class="examples-subtitle">A handful of things abjects are good at. Some of these you can do elsewhere; all of them, here, you own.</p>

    <div class="examples-grid">
      {examples.map((e) => (
        <div class="card example-card">
          <span class="example-glyph">{e.glyph}</span>
          <h3 class="example-title">{e.title}</h3>
          <p class="example-body">{e.body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="examples-footer">Free. Local. Yours. <a href="#downloads">Download Abject</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .examples-section {
    background: transparent;
  }

  .examples-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: -1.5rem auto 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .examples-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .examples-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .example-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .example-glyph {
    display: inline-block;
    align-self: flex-start;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--eldritch);
    background: var(--eldritch-glow);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-accent);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .example-title {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .example-body {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .examples-footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .examples-footer a {
    color: var(--eldritch-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(43, 204, 110, 0.3);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .examples-footer a:hover {
    color: var(--eldritch);
    border-bottom-color: var(--eldritch);
  }

  .examples-footer em {
    color: var(--void-purple);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
